            <p class="ml-4">$\text{Rec}(f) = \mathbb{R} \setminus \{2\}$ (as√≠ntota horizontal $y=2$)</p>
            <p class="ml-4">$\text{Dom}(f^{-1}) = \mathbb{R} \setminus \{2\}$ ‚úì (coincide con $\text{Rec}(f)$)</p>
            
            <p><strong>Paso 7 [Verificar composici√≥n]:</strong></p>
            <p class="ml-4">$(f \circ f^{-1})(x) = f\left(\displaystyle\frac{x+3}{x-2}\right) = \displaystyle\frac{2 \cdot \frac{x+3}{x-2} + 3}{\frac{x+3}{x-2} - 1}$</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Simplificando: $= \displaystyle\frac{2(x+3) + 3(x-2)}{(x+3) - (x-2)} = \frac{2x+6+3x-6}{5} \cdot \frac{5}{1} = x$ ‚úì</p>
            
